      <byline class="print_byline">By Mallery Lane</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Lane, Mallery</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Comment on card-sized, silver-plated bottle opener from jewelry designer Kathy Korvin (Currents); photo (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The jewelry designer Kathy Korvin is one of those chic Parisians who moved to Provence for a healthier life. Now she nips north to Paris on the high-speed train as little as possible, she says, yet business has never been better. This summer, everyone at picnics and outdoor tables seems to be carrying her credit-card-size, silver-plated bottle opener, right; $75, only from Kathy Korvin, 13, rue de Tournon, Paris. Perhaps soon at www.kathykorvin.com.</p>
      </block>
